From: Tommi <tommi@webrtc.org>
Date: Fri, 13 Mar 2026 19:35:01 +0100
Subject: (cherry-pick-branch-heads/7727) [M147] Fix missing mediaSourceId in
 simulcast outbound-rtp stats
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

When simulcast is enabled, only the primary SSRC was mapped to the
sender's attachment ID in TrackMediaInfoMap. This resulted in missing
mediaSourceId properties for secondary simulcast outgoing stats. Updated
TrackMediaInfoMap to map all valid SSRCs provided in the sender's
RtpParameters.

(cherry picked from commit a7f267f8b01ad6a2a11eced7267e61eff932b2ab)

Bug: webrtc:492108787
Fixes: webrtc:492108787
